findings.problemShort: elements must meet minimum color contrast ratio thresholds
findings.solutionShort: ensure the contrast between foreground and background colors meets wcag 2 aa minimum contrast ratio thresholds
findings.solutionLong:
Fix any of the following:
  Element has insufficient color contrast of 2.64 (foreground color: #ffffff, background color: #36aadd, font size: 36.0pt (48px), font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 3:1

findings.solutionShort: ensure interactive controls are not nested as they are not always announced by screen readers or can cause focus problems for assistive technologies
